Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Atok National High School in the Municipality of Atok, Province of Benguet, to Jose Mencio National High School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 334
An Act Changing the Name of the Atok National High School in the Municipality of Atok, Province of Benguet, to Jose Mencio National High School
Section 1. The name of the Atok National High School in the Municipality of Atok, Province of Benguet, is changed to Jose Mencio National High School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 19, 1983
